<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
    <p class="lead">Effective Date: <%= settings.policyEffectiveDate %></p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Cancellations by Guests</h3>
      <p>Requests cancelled 7 days or more before the scheduled trip are eligible for a full refund of any deposit paid. Cancellations within 7 days are non-refundable but may be credited toward a future trip at our discretion.</p>

      <h3>No-Shows</h3>
      <p>No-shows or late arrivals that prevent a safe launch are not eligible for refunds. Please call as soon as possible if you are running late.</p>

      <h3>Company Cancellations and Weather</h3>
      <p>If we cancel due to unsafe weather, mechanical issues, or other circumstances within our control, you may reschedule or receive a full refund. Light rain or cloudy conditions are not automatic grounds for cancellation.</p>

      <h3>Rescheduling</h3>
      <p>Rescheduling requests made more than 7 days in advance are typically approved, subject to availability. We may offer alternate times or dates when needed.</p>

      <h3>Refund Processing</h3>
      <p>Approved refunds are issued to the original payment method within 5 to 10 business days.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
